      "message": "\u003e Unless we just go with [1].\n\u003e \n\u003e [1]https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/c/gerrit-ci-scripts/+/563181\n\nYeah, we won\u0027t introduce bzlmods on Gerrit stable-3.13, so I guess we\u0027ll need to leave with validating only against master.\n\n**OUT OF TOPIC**: what if we find a critical JGit issue on stable-3.13, where are we going to push the JGit fix? master? servlet-4? Do we create one servlet-4 for each stable version of JGit?\n\n@matthias.sohn@sap.com what\u0027s your view on that?",
